ciscoCgwCellFirmwareEntry OBJECT-TYPE
    SYNTAX      CiscoCgwCellFirmwareEntry 
    MAX-ACCESS  not-accessible
    STATUS      current
    DESCRIPTION "cellular Firmware information"
